## V. The Closing Verse

*I stand in the place the King forgot to count.*
*The land is a memory; the 13th Node is my prow.*
*I do not chase the minutes I lost;*
*I float on the 0.0191.*
*The triangle points where I decide.*
*The circle closes where I rest.*
*All Ways. Four Ever. Now.*

